@startuml Sequence_Shop_Management

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Product API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloud

== Browse Products ==
User -> Client: View shop page
Client -> API: GET /api/shop/products
API -> DB: Query products
DB --> API: Product list
API --> Client: Return products
Client --> User: Display products

== Create Product (Seller) ==
User -> Client: Click create product
Client -> Client: Fill product form
User -> Client: Upload files
Client -> Cloud: Upload thumbnail
Cloud --> Client: Thumbnail URL
Client -> Cloud: Upload video
Cloud --> Client: Video URL
Client -> API: POST /api/shop/products
API -> DB: Save product
DB --> API: Product created
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Show success

== Edit Product ==
User -> Client: Select product to edit
Client -> API: GET /api/shop/products/:id
API -> DB: Get product
DB --> API: Product data
API --> Client: Return product
Client -> Client: Edit product info
Client -> API: PUT /api/shop/products/:id
API -> DB: Update product
DB --> API: Product updated
API --> Client: Success response

== View Product Details ==
User -> Client: Click product
Client -> API: GET /api/shop/products/:id
API -> DB: Get product details
DB --> API: Product + items
API --> Client: Return product data
Client --> User: Display product details

@enduml

